{
  "texts": [
    "IAE, ISE, ITAE, and ITSE have been computed as popular indexes.",
    "However, their performance is not the same.",
    "Accordingly, an optimization algorithm can be incorporated into QL and DQNL algorithms to adjust the IAE, ISE, ITAE, and ITSE for both RL controllers.According to the results presented in Table 8, it can be inferred that the RMSE serves as a critical parameter for evaluating the effectiveness of the controllers.",
    "The QL algorithm yields significantly more precise control outcomes, demonstrating an improvement percentage of 39.72% and 5.77% in terms of RMSE relative to the PID and LQR controllers, respectively.",
    "Moreover, the DQNL algorithm yields significantly more precise control outcomes, demonstrating an improvement percentage of 40.29% and 6.66% in terms of RMSE relative to the PID and LQR controllers, respectively."
  ]
}